{"tid":2408048,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本據報擬引入運輸艦　向南西諸島陸上自衛隊運送物資","createTime":"2021-02-14T14:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T14:41:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6b8043a1db468815106ef5f6a01209869e1157","tid":2408048,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.mdc.idv.tw/mdc/navy/jmsdf/lst4002-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdc.idv.tw%2Fmdc%2Fnavy%2Fjmsdf%2Flst4002-4.jpg&h=1b0ee97a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本政府據報計劃在2024年引入3艘中型和小型運輸艦，向部署在南西諸島的陸上自衛隊運送物資，是首次向陸上自衛隊配備運輸艦。<br />\n<br />\n共同社報道，鑑於中國公務船多次駛入尖閣諸島，即是中國稱的釣魚島附近，加上中國實施《海警法》容許海警局船隻使用武器，日方對發生不測事態的擔憂高漲，日方將構建通往離島的彈藥、燃料和食品的穩定供應網，期望透過提高輸送能力來提升機動力，強化陸上自衛隊的應對能力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575675-20210214.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575675-20210214.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eW%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=e1ed4e02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575675-20210214.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=09fcbb6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575675-20210214.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"248742794a2b60a1f10bd6a7978f5c00b59b2a1c","tid":2408048,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:41:41.000Z","msg":"會唔會比海盜打劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}